{"id":319569,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-西部博览会在成都召开，成都访民多人被/","date":"2013-10-24T16:34:31Z","modified":"2013-10-24T16:34:31Z","title":"维权网 | 西部博览会在成都召开，成都访民多人被旅游（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span></span><span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员许枫报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>23</span></span><span>号成都青白江访民林德琼、王于英、金牛彭天惠、新津谢志勇、张小兰、盛素芬到西博会参观！结果，被带到派出所限制自由，直到晚上七点后，才被释放回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24</span></span><span>日，成都青白江访民林德琼到新会展中心去参加，当地政府派了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>个人寸步不离的给她跟着，在她忍无可忍的情况下在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>号参馆举了牌，自己便报了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>，随后跟</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>到了新会展派出所作笔录。</span><span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></span><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>而成都访民黄莉、帅正秀，叶俊华、周成群、李廷惠、王蓉文等人全部被旅游，除王蓉文目前直到在巴中外其他没有任何消息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>据中国西部博览会官网报道称：第十四届中国西部国际博览会开幕式暨第六届中国西部国际合作论坛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>23</span></span><span>日在成都举行，中国国务院副总理汪洋出席论坛并作主旨演讲。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>澳大利亚总督昆廷·布赖斯，加拿大总督戴维·约翰斯顿，马其顿总统格奥尔盖·伊万诺夫，蒙古国总理诺罗布·阿勒坦呼亚格，坦桑尼亚总理米增戈·平达，白俄罗斯副总理托吉克·阿纳托利，法国参议院副议长、前总理让</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>&#8211;</span></span><span>皮埃尔·拉法兰等多国政要出席论坛，并分别作主题演讲。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>据悉，本届西博会将持续至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>27</span></span><span>日，并首次设立主宾国，确定由蒙古国担任；轮值主席单位为云南省；主题市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>(</span></span><span>州</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>)</span></span><span>为四川省阿坝州；首次在县级城市——汶川县设立分会场，举行系列活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span><span></span><br /><span>也就是说：成都当局对访民的监控，一直会延续到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>27</span></span><span>日，一个国际盛会，成了成都上访人的人权灾难。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-J-iPSwuU2w8/Umkjibais1I/AAAAAAAAp9A/g0kJO4tTo-8/s1600/%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-J-iPSwuU2w8/Umkjibais1I/AAAAAAAAp9A/g0kJO4tTo-8/s400/%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></span></div>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DzBxtm2-hFs/Umkjo1JAc8I/AAAAAAAAp9I/AmiLF04zDSY/s1600/%25E9%259D%2592%25E7%2599%25BD%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DzBxtm2-hFs/Umkjo1JAc8I/AAAAAAAAp9I/AmiLF04zDSY/s400/%25E9%259D%2592%25E7%2599%25BD%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591.jpg\" width=\"225\" /></a></span></div>\n<p></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}